      <section eId="section_9">
        <heading><b>Annex B - Hansard References</b></heading>
        <paragraph>
          <num>204 </num>
          <content>
            <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act's passage through Parliament.</p>
            <table uk:widths="1.71in 1.44in 3.15in">
              <tr>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Hansard Reference</b></p>
                </th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Lords</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
